</a>
</div>
<p><br /><br /><br /></p>

<ol>
  <li>Search Wines: Descriptive Analysis
    <ul>
      <li>By leveraging dplyr and ggplot2, we created an interactive dashboard that shows key information about wines, price and rating statistics, and positions of those wines upon the wines that users manaully search on the search bar.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

